I still like the idea of an audio sampler capturing your own voice to 
use as the raw audio then slice and scramble it than play it back. It 
would be a real time hardware version of EVP Maker. It wouldn&#39;t rely 
on radio reception and if the spirits are able to manipulate 
the &quot;randomness&quot; of the scramble then it could be interesting.

