Frank Sumption wrote:&gt;&gt; Now all we need is a pic chip to output 
random numbers which can be used to turn on and off switches that 
allow fixed tones through to a mixer/amplifier---Instant Spiricom! 
I&#39;m thinking use op amp square wave generators, and switch them in 
and out using something like the old 4066 chips. The goal being to 
have a system that works without the presence of radio stations, such 
as remote investigations, and eliminate the concern that we&#39;re just 
creating the messages in our minds trying make sense out of random 
voice fragments.&gt;&gt; Frank-S&gt;
